Class DataObjectGroup

    DataObject

    public class DataObjectGroup
extends DataObjectPackageIdElement
implements DataObject
    The Class DataObjectGroup.

    Class for SEDA element DataObjectGroup. It contains logbook metadata and links to contained DataObjects binary or physical.

        public DataObjectGroup(DataObjectPackage dataObjectPackage,

        Instantiates a new DataObjectGroup.

        If DataObjectPackage is defined the new ArchiveUnit is added with a generated uniqID in the structure.

        Parameters:
        dataObjectPackage - the DataObjectPackage containing the DataObjectGroup
        path - the path defining the ArchiveUnit onDisk representation or null

      • idFromSedaXml

        public static String idFromSedaXml(SEDAXMLEventReader xmlReader,
                                   DataObjectPackage dataObjectPackage,
                                   String rootDir,
                                   SEDALibProgressLogger sedaLibProgressLogger)
                            throws SEDALibException,
                                   InterruptedException
        Import the DataObjectGroup in XML expected form form the SEDA Manifest in the ArchiveTransfer and return it's id in ArchiveTransfer.
        Parameters:
        xmlReader - the SEDAXMLEventReader reading the SEDA manifest
        dataObjectPackage - the DataObjectPackage to be completed
        rootDir - the directory where the BinaryDataObject files are exported
        sedaLibProgressLogger - the progress logger
        Returns:
        the inDataPackageObjectId of the read DataObjectGroup, or null if not a DataObjectGroup
        Throws:
        SEDALibException - if the XML can't be read or the SEDA scheme is not respected
        InterruptedException - if export process is interrupted
